<title type="html"><![CDATA[1 ppu cycle != 1 pixel ?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=662&amp;p=5571#p5571"><![CDATA[
There are 341 PPU ticks in one scanline. The first 256 ticks correspond directly to the 256 rendered pixels; the remaining 85 ticks correspond to HBLANK.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Sun Oct 16, 2005 8:00 pm</p><hr />
